# Liabilities Provisions Total Excluding Provisions For Loans And Leases Amount

## identifier
de15016

## type
float

## definition
This is the value of total provisions (an accounting entry for liabilities of uncertain timing or amount). For reporting purposes exclude any individual or collective provisions relating to loans and finance leases.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Liabilities.Provisions.TotalExcludingProvisionsForLoansAndLeases.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo6.02.19
- period=instant
